commit_message:
Verify get extension attributes of V2/V3 APIs

This patch adds the JSON schema for Nova V2/V3 get extension APIs
includes the attributes to block the backward incompatibility change
in the future.

The response body of v2 is the below:
{
    "extension": {
        "updated": "2011-06-09T00:00:00+00:00",
        "name": "Multinic",
        "links": [],
        "namespace": "http://xxx.xxx.xxx/xxx/xxx",
        "alias": "NMN",
        "description": "Multiple network support."
    }
}

The response body of v3 is the below:
{
    "extension": {
        "name": "Multinic",
        "alias": "NMN",
        "description": "Multiple network support.",
        "version": 1
    }
}

Change-Id: I79ae09636bfe943c2d0792c796c271f400515c16

Check detail list Images attributes of Nova V2 API

This patch adds the JSON Schema for response of Nova V2 detail list
